queries: select count(user) as users, count(user.events) as events from schema quo

select
	monthofyear(month(user.sessions.startTime)) as Month,
	theyear(year(user.sessions.startTime)) as Year,
	count(user) as users, 
	count(user.sessions) as sessions, 
	count(user.sessions.events) as events
from schema quo
